50
00:03:32,239 --> 00:03:34,720
Tableau was the like the biggest in the market.

51
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:40,319
They had like numerous features but the core feature which is basically content creation piece was not that great.

52
00:03:40,319 --> 00:03:48,959
And after studying all these products, I realized the demand in the market is so much that even products like these are able to like earn revenue.

53
00:03:48,959 --> 00:03:52,239
So I realized like I can serve this demand really well.

54
00:03:52,239 --> 00:03:52,799
>> All right, cool.

