One of the co-founder of Rocket Up, Charlie actually saw our journey on LinkedIn and he actually reached out to us.

64
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:30,560
We would love to help you launch uh Supergrow on Rocket Up.

65
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:41,680
