So the basic pricing tier was $79 which basically translate to our basic plan right now.

74
00:04:59,199 --> 00:05:02,479
The second plan was $199 which is a pro plan.

75
00:05:02,479 --> 00:05:05,360
The third plan was the agency plan which was $299.

76
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:13,840
So whoever bought the product back then they were getting like 4 to 5 years of value just by paying like $299 $199.

77
00:05:13,840 --> 00:05:14,080
>> Okay.

78
