91
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:08,319
Essentially our role was build the product and the second was support which is really crucial for entity because you are going to get lot of queries and stuff.

92
00:06:08,319 --> 00:06:10,080
So those were the only two things which we did.

93
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:12,960
Everything regarding marketing was actually done by rocketub.

94
00:06:12,960 --> 00:06:19,120
So for this rocketup took like 40% of the cut which translates to around $40,000 for us.

95
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:20,240
Obviously, it's a big cut.

96
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:21,680
40% is a huge cut.

97
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:26,160
But if you think about it, at that moment, we did not have like we had only like one or two customers.

98
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:33,440
We had almost close to $0, but just by launching our product through them, we were able to generate $40,000.

99
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:33,680
Okay.

100
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:40,639
Wow, that's a big cut, 40%, I imagine a lot of people watching this are like, why would you give up that much of a product that you built?

101
00:06:40,639 --> 00:06:44,880
