00:13:21,680 --> 00:13:24,240
>> For app I use rails, react and tailwind.

203
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:25,680
I use Postgress for DB.

204
00:13:25,680 --> 00:13:28,399
Superbase for O and uh like assets.

205
00:13:28,399 --> 00:13:33,200
Railway for hosting, framer for landing page, superguri for LinkedIn content creation,

206
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:40,000
intercom for live chat, mix panel for product analytics, Stripe for payments, and Microsoft clarity for session recordings.

207
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:45,040
>> Could you also, if you're comfortable sharing, break down some of the costs and margins to run this business?

